title: Derek & Brandon Fiechter - Anime Tales WebRip [FLAC]
description:
Listen to beautiful piano-based music, each piece expressing different emotions like happiness, sorrow, romance, and others.

Anime Tales is beautiful anime piano music about a young lady who is forced to flee her village and sets off on a journey to seek for a better life. While on her journey, she ends up making three friends who protect her from her enemies and keep her safe from danger.

Derek & Brandon Fiechter are two composers who enjoy making music which transports people to mystical worlds and lands.
